fullText: welcome to Epic mint leaes your channel for mind-blowing vegan recipes sugarfree oil free da free high protein lowfat soft inside crunchy outside super healthy super delicious chocolate truffles made with chickpeas but no chickpea taste don't worry just pure chocolate travel flavor so good so hit the Subscribe button and let's get started first off open of chickp drain R and throw them into a foood processor along with a/4 cup of cocoa powder six metal dates and two tablesp of peanut butter next blend it until [Applause] smooth now roll the dough into little bite-sized balls and throw them into melted terree dark chocolate let them cool in the fridge and enjoy the super healthy and super tasty chocolate truffles thanks for watching
